author: Sam Whiting
title: McMurtry Building completes Stanford Arts District
text:
Photo: Liz Hafalia, The Chronicle A view of the McMurtry Building seen from the Rodin Sculpture garden in Stanford, Calif., on Friday, September 25, 2015. A view of the McMurtry Building seen from the Rodin Sculpture...
In the lobby of the angular new McMurtry Building at Stanford University hangs a rectangle of fake lawn with “5.05” stamped into it. Any incoming freshman knows the meaning of this number.
